parameters: First time in \C[6]Old Raven's Keep\C[0]? It might look like
a dump, but we call it home.

myself". So like most poor people, I ended up here in \C[6]Old
That's horrible! Don't the royal family or the people of the
city do anything to help the poor?
Those stuck up rich folk? Ha! They just shove the poor and destitute
out in the cold to die. So when you've got nowhere else to go,
I'd re-start this fire and cook something to eat if I had
anything to cook. Oh well, another day in \C[6]Old Raven's Keep\C[0].
